                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">Stavanger, 24 August 2010</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[24.08.2010]</p>
                <p>"We are facing major challenges in the energy sector. If we are to meet our energy needs and achieve our environmental goals, both the energy industry and the government must do their part", the Prime Minister stated at the ONS conference in Stavanger.</p>
                
                
